messages.content: Hi! How can I help you today?

Hi! I actually need some help with an order I placed. I ordered some home office items and some hiking gear because I was planning to work remotely from my parent's place in Seattle and enjoy the outdoors. But now my company is making us go back to the office soon. I was wondering if it's possible to cancel just the office items from my order and keep the hiking gear. If that's possible, I'd like to know how much I'll get refunded and have the refund go back to my original payment method. If partial cancellation isn't possible, then I'd like to keep the order but update my default address to my parent's place in Seattle. Can you help me with this?
